<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="max" id="max">max</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Синтаксис:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;algorithm&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> max<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> x, <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> y <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> max<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> x, <span class="kw4">const</span> T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> y, BinPred p <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Функция max() возвращает наибольшее значение из двух: x и y.
</p>

<p>
Если задан бинарный предикат p, то ониспользуется вместо оператора &lt; для сравнения двух элементов.
</p>

<p>
Например, следующий фрагмент кода реализует различные варианты использования функции max():
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">   <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Max of 1 and 9999 is &quot;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> max<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu0">1</span>, <span class="nu0">9999</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy4">;</span>
   <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Max of 'a' and 'b' is &quot;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> max<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">'a'</span>, <span class="st0">'b'</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy4">;</span>
   <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Max of 3.14159 and 2.71828 is &quot;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> max<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu16">3.14159</span>, <span class="nu16">2.71828</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Этот код выводит:
</p>
<pre class="code">
   Max of 1 and 9999 is 9999
   Max of 'a' and 'b' is b
   Max of 3.14159 and 2.71828 is 3.14159</pre>
<p>
Смотрите также: <a href="max_element" class="wikilink1" title="ru:algorithm:max_element">max_element</a>, <a href="min" class="wikilink1" title="ru:algorithm:min">min</a>, <a href="min_element" class="wikilink1" title="ru:algorithm:min_element">min_element</a>
</p>

